HEADWORD: conditioning
<hw>conditioning</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a learning process in which an
organism's behavior becomes dependent on the occurrence of a stimulus in
its environment. See <er>conditioned response</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

